{"tid":392600,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"BoJack Horseman Season 4 出咗","createTime":"2017-09-08T15:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T06:11:41.000Z","uid":78390,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73a5ef91525f7f217828b283c2ba7f1e27d76185","tid":392600,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"Misery is the New Comedy<br />\n<br />\n故事講述一個過氣九十年代嘅電視名星 希望在事業上找尋新嘅高琒<br />\n不過係找尋時 原來過去二十年都一無事處 對朋友對自己都未誠實過 最自豪還是二十年前的他<br />\n每一集都好似打開BoJack黑暗一面 明白自己的過錯 但Bojack又一一重複錯誤<br />\n呢部劇挑戰好多問題例如政治，媒體的虛偽<br />\n但最令人最愛BoJack這套劇就係如何打開觀眾黑暗的一面 有冇曾經離棄朋友 放棄自己良知去達到某一個位置 只想聽想聽的話"},{"pid":"cd9f4cb7b0d8800bae74856a7a4fd14c650f8ce2","tid":392600,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:10:11.000Z","msg":"要總括這部劇<br />\n我諗Mr. Peanutbutter 講得最好<br />\n<br />\nMr. Peanutbutter: The universe is a cruel, uncaring void. The key to being happy isn't the search for meaning; is to just keep yourself busy with unimportant nonsense, and eventually, you will be dead."},{"pid":"8bc039839f4f10da6646ae61c361c8c829a925f4","tid":392600,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wljekf2g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwljekf2g&h=936ed499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d56eb63d5b3ec2e38897c9b466304b51e91bca71","tid":392600,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef017302112cfe0c6c1b002fc4a0eb93fdf897be","tid":392600,"uid":40350,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"呢套垃圾竟然都有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edb90e681cf730ff8fe61c3987d513f2c599405","tid":392600,"uid":82532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08